flavor_text: Munna always float in the air. People whose dreams are eaten by them forget what the dreams had been about.
It eats the dreams of people and Pokemon. When it eats a pleasant dream it expels pink-colored mist.
This Pokemon appears before people and Pokemon who are having nightmares and eats those dreams.
